Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The Lake Houston region consists of several growing communities. From gold courses to country living and from upscale mixed-use developments to signature shopping, the Lake Houston Area has it all. With the recreation of Lake Houston and the San Jacinto River, the proximity of Bush IAH and the Port of Houston, and the quality of its many subdivisions, the area has proven to be a strong attraction to newcomers. Abundant health care and exemplary schools add to the appeal while developments like Kingwood Parc, Kings Creek, Generation Park and Grand Texas Theme Park offer promise years to come.
